kings, where witches and warlocks can endearingly twist the fates of total
strangers to determine the outcome of an evening.  It's a place where the most
talented performers and musicians from all walks of life come to shine for one
glorious moment.  Intricate, fading designs cover the crimson red walls of the
theatre.  False gold columns run the length of the walls, stretching up into
the heavens.  The house waits before you to the west.    ~
